From 8e251efc8877b4c62b6b129799245bc707cb6647 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 10:50:12 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: AI service v4 + profile avatars + UI overhaul + Swift 6
 fixes

AI Service (Plink/Services/AIService.swift):
- Replace dead OpenRouter free model IDs (deepseek free tier removed,
  gemini-2.0-flash-exp deprecated) with 7 verified-working models led by
  openrouter/free meta-router
- Add 429 retry logic respecting retry_after_seconds (default 5s, cap 30s)
- Bump max_tokens 1024 -> 2048 for reasoning models
- Make Message.content/reasoning optional, fallback content -> reasoning
- Apply same fallback chain to chatStream() (was: single model, no retry)
- Empirically verified end-to-end against real OpenRouter API

Profile & Avatars:
- New AvatarView.swift component with initials placeholder fallback
- New AdminBadge imageset
- ProfileViewModel: +213 lines for avatar upload + display
- ProfileView: full redesign (+473/-152)

UI overhaul:
- MainTabView redesign (+377/-185)
- BioluminescentBackground: 5x larger, smoother animation (+357/-30)
- SettingsView, PrivacySettingsView, NotificationsView restructured
- RoomChatView, RoomView, VideoContainerView polish
- Color+Theme + View+Extensions: new design tokens

Concurrency (Swift 6 strict mode):
- New MutexBox<T> wrapper for mutable state in nonisolated contexts
- SyncEngine, WebSocketClient, APIClient: Swift 6 Sendable fixes

Other:
- Info.plist: new plist keys for AI service + permissions
- LocalizationManager: minor fix
- AuthService, AuthViewModel: token refresh hardening

Excluded: backend-rooms-fix.ts (TS file, belongs to backend repo)
